flyingbirds
===========

Flying birds Simulation using uC++ and openGL

Before make, make sure you have uC++ installed as well as OpenGL

Installing uC++
===============

sudo cp u++6.0.0.sh /usr/local/bin

cd /usr/local/bin

sudo sh u++-6.0.0.sh 

Installing OpenGL
==================
sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev

